            <p>Paste the exact question you want to answer to ensure maximum relevance.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Specify Your Area of Expertise</span>
            <p>Guide the AI to match the right tone, depth, and authority by providing details about your background.</p>
          </li>
